metadata.title: Tangram's New Dallas Showroom
metadata.description: We are thrilled to share our new East Quarter Showroom with the DFW community. The design is a reflection of the surrounding neighborhood, its historical ties to the automotive industry, and Tangram's creative culture. With subtle nods to the 1920s, the design is a translation of "Old Meets New."
